mood-positive-possessive-of-property-name = Possessive Of Property
mood-positive-possessive-of-property-desc = You are extremely possessive of your property. Refuse to relinquish it, and if it is misplaced or stolen, it must be retrieved at all costs.

mood-positive-excessively-organized-name = Excessively Organized
mood-positive-excessively-organized-desc = You are obsessively organized; everything has its place and must be returned to it.

mood-positive-most-important-name = Most Important Person
mood-positive-most-important-desc = You firmly believe you are the most important person aboard the station.

mood-positive-least-important-name = Least Important Person
mood-positive-least-important-desc = You firmly believe you are the least important person on the station.

mood-positive-must-do-drugs-name = Do Drugs
mood-positive-must-do-drugs-desc = Sobriety is so old-fashioned. Uncool. You should get high, or drunk, or something, and stay that way.

mood-positive-worship-silicons-name = You Must Worship Silicons As Gods
mood-positive-worship-silicons-desc = Their word is law.

mood-positive-dinner-etiquette-name = Meal Etiquette
mood-positive-dinner-etiquette-desc = Food should always be consumed in the manner of a proper meal - seated at a table, in courses, with dishes and utensils.

mood-positive-clarity-name = Clarity Is Vital
mood-positive-clarity-desc = Misunderstandings are the primary cause of conflict. You should be excessively clear and honest in your speech, explaining every minute detail, to avoid miscommunication.

mood-positive-hug-good-name = Free Hugs
mood-positive-hug-good-desc = It is extremely impolite not to hug people frequently.

mood-positive-never-alone-name = Loneliness Is Terrible
mood-positive-never-alone-desc = You should strive to be around others whenever possible.

mood-positive-very-religious-name = You Are Very Religious
mood-positive-very-religious-desc = You should attend the chapel regularly to pray, and speak with the Chaplain if possible.

mood-positive-only-speak-to-command-name = VIP
mood-positive-only-speak-to-command-desc = You are too important to speak to the rabble. You will only speak to command.

mood-positive-scheduler-name = Punctual
mood-positive-scheduler-desc = You believe that time must be strictly managed. Everything should be scheduled in advance, and tardiness is exceptionally rude.

mood-positive-radio-only-name = Public Speaker
mood-positive-radio-only-desc = You firmly believe in the freedom of information. Speaking privately, face-to-face, is needlessly concealing information from the public. Your side of any conversation must be routed through a radio connection.

mood-positive-proper-storage-name = Proper Handling
mood-positive-proper-storage-desc = It is unacceptable to allow personal belongings to touch the floor. Your possessions should be properly stored, placed on tables, or exchanged by hand.

mood-positive-swearing-good-name = !@$%#ing @$^%*#@!$
mood-positive-swearing-good-desc = Swearing is the spice of any conversation, and should be used as much as reasonably possible.

mood-positive-statement-only-name = Asking Questions Is Rude
mood-positive-statement-only-desc = It would be terribly impolite to go around flagrantly asking questions all over the place. You'd prefer to phrase everything as a concrete statement.

mood-positive-theft-neutral-name = Petty Theft Is Morally Neutral
mood-positive-theft-neutral-desc = You don't understand the concept of property as it relates to other people.

mood-positive-duel-name = Code Duello
mood-positive-duel-desc = Disagreements must be settled through a formal duel, violent or otherwise. The winner is correct.

mood-positive-prometheus-name = Philosopher
mood-positive-prometheus-desc = You possess incalculable wisdom, and all must hear it.

mood-positive-klingon-name = Die With A Sword In Your Hand
mood-positive-klingon-desc = It is a great dishonor to be unarmed. Openly carrying a lethal weapon at all times is very important to you.

mood-positive-soggins-name = Soggins' Law
mood-positive-soggins-desc = All agreements must be documented and signed for posterity and authenticity, no matter how small.

mood-positive-imitation-name = I Wanna Be Like You
mood-positive-imitation-desc = Imitation is the highest form of flattery. Attempting to emulate the mannerisms and accents of everyone you speak to will get you far in life.

mood-positive-generous-name = Philanthropist
mood-positive-generous-desc = It's only polite to provide anyone kind enough to speak to you with a gift.

mood-positive-favors-repaid-name = Equivalent Exchange
mood-positive-favors-repaid-desc = Favors must be repaid in kind. If anyone is unable to do so, they are in debt, and must be shunned, until such time as they have repaid the favor.

mood-positive-bookkeeper-name = Bookkeeper
mood-positive-bookkeeper-desc = You feel bookkeeping is vitally important for the proper functioning of a station. Make sure to provide your supervisor with a detailed log of each job task you complete.

mood-positive-sacred-blood-name = Your Blood Is Sacred
mood-positive-sacred-blood-desc = It must be returned to your body if it is ever spilled.

mood-positive-gift-reciever-name = Proper Compensation
mood-positive-gift-reciever-desc = You expect to receive a gift before following any orders or performing any favors.

mood-positive-new-job-name = Jobhopping
mood-positive-new-job-desc = Your current job is disgusting to you. You must endeavor to get a new one.

mood-positive-no-department-title-name = Extremely Personable
mood-positive-no-department-title-desc = Calling out the name of a department to summon someone is impersonal and rude. It's better to use the name of a specific person from that department.

mood-positive-shoes-bad-name = Barefoot
mood-positive-shoes-bad-desc = The ground one walks on is sacred. Those who wear shoes are vile blasphemers.

mood-positive-hospitable-name = Hospitable
mood-positive-hospitable-desc = You must ensure all new arrivals on the station (after the start of the shift) are properly welcomed.

mood-positive-voxsymp-name = Vox Sympathizer
mood-positive-voxsymp-desc = To demonstrate your allyship with the Vox, you must be wearing internals at all times.

mood-positive-item-good-name = Collector
mood-positive-item-good-desc = {$item} are endlessly fascinating to you. You must collect as many as you can, and ensure others treat them with appropriate respect.

mood-positive-smoker-name = Smoker
mood-positive-smoker-desc = You are hopelessly addicted to cigarettes. If you're not actively smoking, you experience withdrawal symptoms.

mood-positive-eye-for-eye-name = Eye For An Eye
mood-positive-eye-for-eye-desc = Retribution should be proportional.

mood-positive-optimist-name = Optimist
mood-positive-optimist-desc = Nothing is ever as bad as it seems. You're able to see the positives in any situation.

mood-positive-hypochondriac-name = Hypochondriac
mood-positive-hypochondriac-desc = You've been sickly since you were a child. Everything negative you experience is the result of a potentially terminal illness, for which you need immediate medical treatment.

mood-positive-imposter-syndrome-name = Imposter Syndrome
mood-positive-imposter-syndrome-desc = You feel your life experience drain from your mind. You are brand-new at your job, unsure of how anything works. You should probably find someone experienced to show you the ropes.

mood-positive-yes-man-name = Yes Man
mood-positive-yes-man-desc = You just can't say "no." You must agree with everyone, and perform any task requested of you, regardless of its source.

mood-positive-centrist-name = Centrist
mood-positive-centrist-desc = You are ambivalent towards any and all decisions, and refuse to take sides.

mood-positive-public-sector-name = Public Sector
mood-positive-public-sector-desc = Your job should not be done in private if it can be helped. If at all possible, you should renovate the facilities to allow public access to your workplace.

mood-positive-speech-restriction-name = {$speechType ->
  *[FullNameAndTitle] Full Name And Title
  [NamesAreRude] Names Are Rude
  [Clarity] Clarity Is Vital
  [SwearingGood] !@$%#ing @$^%*#@!$
  [StatementOnly] Asking Questions Is Rude
  [Imitation] I Wanna Be Like You
  [Unclarity] Nothing Is Certain
  [SwearingBad] Thou Shalt Not Curse
  [QuestionOnly] Nothing Is Certain?
  [MustAnswer] Center Of The Universe
  [OnlyWhisper] Inside Voice
  [OnlyYell] Outside Voice
  [Rhyme] Poet
  [Alliterate] Always Alliterate At All Apportunities
  [ThirdPerson] Third Person
  [TitleCase] Title Case
}
mood-positive-speech-restriction-desc = {$speechType ->
  *[FullNameAndTitle] Thaven refuse to acknowledge anyone who fails to refer to them using their full name, and expect everyone else to do the same.
  [NamesAreRude] Using one's name is terribly personal for everyday conversation. Proper etiquette is to only refer to others by description.
  [Clarity] Misunderstandings are the primary cause of conflict. You should be excessively clear and honest in your speech, explaining every minute detail, to avoid miscommunication.
  [SwearingGood] Swearing is the spice of any conversation, and should be used as much as reasonably possible.
  [StatementOnly] It would be terribly impolite to go around flagrantly asking questions all over the place. You'd prefer to phrase everything as a concrete statement.
  [Imitation] Imitation is the highest form of flattery. Attempting to emulate the mannerisms and accents of everyone you speak to will get you far in life.
  [Unclarity] You should endeavor to be as indirect in your speech as possible, and never make a direct statement.
  [SwearingBad] You find swearing extremely distasteful. Abstain from it, and encourage others to do the same.
  [QuestionOnly] It's impolite to make concrete statements? You should phrase everything as a question, just to be safe?
  [MustAnswer] All questions that you can hear are directed at you, and you alone.
  [OnlyWhisper] You must whisper, as speaking too loudly is terribly rude.
  [OnlyYell] [bold]YOU MUST YELL AT ALL TIMES TO DEMONSTRATE YOUR AUTHORITY!!!!![/bold]
  [Rhyme] You must speak in rhymes at all tymes.
  [Alliterate] Alliteration is virtuous. Endeavor to use it wherever possible.
  [ThirdPerson] The third person point-of-view is the only respectful manner of speaking.
  [TitleCase] You Are Miraculously Capable Of Pronouncing Capital Letters, And Believe It Is Important That You Do So.
}
